{"tid":1477875,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"因爲父母細個冇整 BN(O) 或者九七後出世嘅你唔好灰心，反而更加應該支持平權","createTime":"2019-08-16T09:24:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T12:10:45.000Z","uid":40641,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"48b5726da7f2e6cbbd065885d2f4205721f9505a","tid":1477875,"uid":40641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T09:24:20.000Z","msg":"最近見啲講 BN(O) 平權嘅 post 好多人話自己細個父母冇幫佢哋整 BN(O)，或者佢哋係九七後出世，所以平權唔關佢哋事。不過好似好多人唔察覺，根據英國國籍法，BC 一般嚟講係可以傳畀唔喺英國領土出世嘅下一代，係要去到傳畀孫嗰代先至唔得。即係話，如果你父母本身有 BN(O) 但你冇，平咗權之後會變咗普通嘅英國國籍，噉順理成章你都會繼承到佢哋個英國籍。<br />\n<br />\n所以假若有一日 BN(O) 平權做 BC，好大機會本身冇 BN(O) 嘅人都可以因爲父母變咗 BC 而變成 BC！唔係話一定得，要睇到時英國 draft 嗰份法令嘅 exact detail，不過一定有希望，所以冇 BN(O) 嘅九十後唔使灰心，呢樣嘢大家都關事！"},{"pid":"6297c310a997efeac7dcf89d6c71d9cab4976523","tid":1477875,"uid":53592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T09:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67cbb3593597d7d11c9c625c2f97f18030820bf9","tid":1477875,"uid":190178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:43:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0499a6da4ef34975f433f8a610d0a257b1e91aa3","tid":1477875,"uid":171718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:44:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eaf654d22aa0a3efe6533636e40fa40cd4808ef9","tid":1477875,"uid":103893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:56:41.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"618c86ac89a40b8029f2976b3c309d1aa527c70d","tid":1477875,"uid":181088,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:59:40.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n首先要老豆老母有<br />\n我2老on99 麥撚都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac08fd43d6f41fe55703c2e572a299318424c4e5","tid":1477875,"uid":34334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T12:00:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4503a63e084456c376357548